    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>做过很多遍了，每次还是得现查，记一下:</p>

<pre><code>echo "'param 1' 'param 2'" | xargs -n1 | xargs -I@ echo \[@\] \[@\]
</code></pre>

<p>output:</p>

<p><code>
[param 1] [param 1]
[param 2] [param 2]
</code></p>

<h2 id="xargs">xargs里面替换字符串</h2>

<pre><code>ls|xargs -I @  echo "mv @ @.pack"|sed 's/.json.pack.pack/.pack/g'|bash
</code></pre>

